text: Regino Campos Hermosisima Jr. (born October 18, 1927) is a Filipino politician and lawyer. He was born in Cebu. He became a member of the Supreme Court as an Associate Justice on July 10, 1995.Testing the Logic of Strategic Defection: The Case of the Philippine Supreme Court—An Empirical Analysis (1986–2010) He retired on October 18, 1997. He was nominated by President Fidel Ramos.The solution to the murder of Aquino has been pending for 26 years ==References== Category:Politicians from Cebu Category:Filipino judges Category:Living people Category:1927 births
